{"title":"环形跑道","authors":["孔和平"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":1,"day":29}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"环形跑道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔和平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有起点，也没有终点，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一圈又一圈，把目标"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铺向无限的遥远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力的节奏，力的旋转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄浑和激越，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灌制成一张博大的唱片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发在旋转中返青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春在旋转中强健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追求在旋转中实现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四百米的环形跑道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋转着一个奋进的主题——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"建设者的生命永恒地伸延。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}